{"tid":826086,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本購物網站ZOZOTOWN社長成 SpaceX全球首名「月球旅客」","createTime":"2018-09-18T04:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T06:53:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99a2626931b2798b30a1505d960b8146d319010d","tid":826086,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537236005_c84e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537236005_c84e.jpg&h=0fab7985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太空探索科技公司SpaceX周一宣佈全球首名「月球旅客」的身份，他就是日本億萬富豪前澤友作。<br />\n<br />\n前澤是日本購物網站ZOZOTOWN社長，據《福布斯》公佈的2018年日本50大富豪榜，估計他坐擁27億美元（210億港元）身家，是日本第18位富有的人。他表示會「包起」SpaceX的BFR火箭的所有座位，計劃2023年邀請6至8位藝術家一同前往月球。他們在感受太空之美後，會共同創作主題為「#dearMoon」的藝術作品。<br />\n<br />\n他熱愛收藏藝術品，曾以天價8.6億美元在蘇富比拍賣行買下紐約已故塗鴉藝術家Jean Michel Basquiat一幅作品，拍賣價創下多項紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n前澤感情生活豐富，年初被雜誌踢爆他秘戀26歲日本女星剛力彩芽，兩人被爆戀情後已大方認愛。"},{"pid":"6107e0977d94178abdaa940db5868f9a9426e66d","tid":826086,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"剛力彩芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b363687c0d19c597679a6a606d923a417ad94d1","tid":826086,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a64c4cc039f46e6de12856baf85468ea5acb2df","tid":826086,"uid":4709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"身家27億買8億既畫<br />\n會唔會啊..."},{"pid":"73d3b3139f845e2fbba18b5742041837741c8335","tid":826086,"uid":145779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6107e0977d94178abdaa940db5868f9a9426e66d","tid":826086,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"剛力彩芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm